WEBVTT

01:49.400 --> 01:52.130
There are so many beautiful things in this world,

01:52.880 --> 01:54.880
but none of them belong to me.

01:56.600 --> 01:58.240
God is so unfair.

01:58.800 --> 02:00.130
You stay at home all day,

02:00.160 --> 02:02.400
and you don't even care about our child's studies.

02:02.400 --> 02:03.280
I did.

02:03.320 --> 02:04.320
What did you do?

02:04.600 --> 02:05.880
Her grades are getting worse.

02:05.880 --> 02:07.610
Is this the result of your care?

02:08.800 --> 02:10.120
I really did.

02:10.400 --> 02:11.660
How dare you talk back!

02:11.960 --> 02:13.680
Talk back? I'll show you!

02:13.880 --> 02:14.480
Talk back!

02:15.240 --> 02:18.560
Stop beating me! Please stop!

02:20.880 --> 02:21.600
Get out!

02:44.640 --> 02:45.760
I'll get the medicine.

02:45.760 --> 02:46.600
No need.

02:47.920 --> 02:48.640
Xiaoyan.

02:50.000 --> 02:52.600
I don't understand why you won't get a divorce.

02:53.360 --> 02:55.090
After every time this happens,

02:55.120 --> 02:56.280
you just cry.

02:56.720 --> 02:58.120
What's the use of crying?

02:58.320 --> 02:59.520
If I get a divorce,

03:00.360 --> 03:01.490
where would we live?

03:03.040 --> 03:04.360
The money is with your dad.

03:04.360 --> 03:05.720
He is not my dad.

03:07.520 --> 03:09.180
I don't have a father like him.

03:09.720 --> 03:10.560
Xiaoyan.

03:11.520 --> 03:12.480
I'm sorry.

03:13.000 --> 03:14.680
It's all my fault.

03:16.880 --> 03:17.840
I'm sorry.

03:22.200 --> 03:23.680
Just divorce him, okay?

03:24.280 --> 03:25.840
I can quit school

03:26.240 --> 03:27.320
and get a job.

03:27.560 --> 03:29.360
We can rent a place to live.

03:30.000 --> 03:31.280
The world is so big.

03:31.960 --> 03:34.440
There must be a place for us.

03:35.040 --> 03:35.920
No.

03:36.560 --> 03:37.720
You have to study.

03:38.400 --> 03:39.860
Once you get into college,

03:40.160 --> 03:41.920
you can leave here.

03:42.440 --> 03:43.480
What about you?

03:44.840 --> 03:46.500
What will you do after I leave?

03:46.880 --> 03:49.540
Half of your life has already been ruined by him.

03:49.640 --> 03:50.640
Mom is fine.

03:52.240 --> 03:53.440
Your dad will change.

03:53.960 --> 03:55.680
He won't change, Mom.

03:56.000 --> 03:57.079
I'm begging you.

03:57.600 --> 04:00.040
Let's leave here, okay?

04:00.760 --> 04:02.680
I can go study in another city.

04:02.760 --> 04:04.480
We can rent a place.

04:04.600 --> 04:07.840
I can work part-time while studying.

04:08.360 --> 04:09.760
You don't need to support me.

04:09.760 --> 04:11.080
I can even support you.

04:11.400 --> 04:13.360
I don't want to live like this anymore.

04:13.360 --> 04:14.720
Mom, I'm begging you.

04:14.760 --> 04:15.520
Really.

04:15.600 --> 04:18.260
Mom, I really can't stand it for another second.

04:19.440 --> 04:21.680
I'm begging you, let's go.

04:23.280 --> 04:25.680
But I can't let you grow up without a father.

04:26.200 --> 04:28.840
I can't let you be a child from a single-parent family.

04:28.840 --> 04:30.040
Would that

04:30.080 --> 04:32.360
be any worse than now?

04:33.520 --> 04:34.400
But...

04:37.000 --> 04:38.960
You still can't leave him, can you?

04:42.360 --> 04:44.280
What are you holding onto?

04:52.320 --> 04:53.320
How could you?

04:54.680 --> 04:55.880
So cowardly.

05:03.000 --> 05:03.880
Xiaoyan.

05:07.840 --> 05:08.720
Xiaoyan.

05:34.240 --> 05:35.040
Qiao Yan.

05:43.400 --> 05:44.240
Yuanbao.

05:47.159 --> 05:47.890
You are here.

05:47.960 --> 05:50.800
Yuanbao, don't be afraid. I am here.

05:57.200 --> 05:58.200
Mutou.

06:01.040 --> 06:01.720
Yuanbao.

06:03.040 --> 06:03.840
Hold on.

06:04.400 --> 06:05.730
Hold on tight behind me.

06:15.480 --> 06:16.240
Yuanbao,

06:17.000 --> 06:17.920
how are you?

06:20.320 --> 06:21.360
I am back.

06:21.840 --> 06:23.720
You are home. It's alright.

06:24.880 --> 06:27.240
Bao, I made you some pork rib soup.

06:27.480 --> 06:28.760
Get up and have some later

06:28.760 --> 06:30.160
to regain your strength.

06:30.200 --> 06:31.320
It will be ready soon.

06:31.320 --> 06:32.560
I'll go check the soup.

06:32.560 --> 06:34.960
Yuanbao, I'll pour you a glass of hot water.

06:39.040 --> 06:40.320
I'm sorry, Grandma.

06:40.840 --> 06:42.000
I made you worry.

06:42.040 --> 06:44.280
Say no more. I know everything.

06:45.680 --> 06:46.880
You know?

06:49.040 --> 06:51.100
Qiao Yan was more conscious than you.

06:51.400 --> 06:52.760
She told us everything.

06:53.960 --> 06:55.290
You did the right thing.

06:56.200 --> 06:57.320
You don't blame me?

06:57.880 --> 07:00.520
It'd be a lie to say I'm not angry or don't blame you.

07:00.520 --> 07:02.240
But thanks to you this time,

07:02.400 --> 07:04.440
otherwise Qiao Yan would be finished,

07:04.440 --> 07:06.300
and their family would be broken.

07:07.480 --> 07:09.560
My granddaughter is so brave.

07:10.600 --> 07:12.400
By the way, how is Qiao Yan?

07:12.640 --> 07:14.720
She's fine. She's gone home.

07:15.240 --> 07:16.320
Gone home?

07:16.720 --> 07:17.640
Don't worry.

07:17.880 --> 07:19.840
Mr. Tian went back with her.

07:20.440 --> 07:22.200
Speaking of Qiao Yan's father,

07:22.360 --> 07:23.690
I'm really speechless.

07:23.760 --> 07:25.840
How could he do such a thing?

07:26.120 --> 07:28.280
No wonder Qiao Yan got depression.

07:29.240 --> 07:30.800
And look at her mother,

07:31.160 --> 07:32.480
so cowardly.

07:33.159 --> 07:34.690
I really don't understand.

07:36.760 --> 07:37.440
Grandma.

07:39.200 --> 07:40.760
I feel so lucky.

07:41.680 --> 07:43.920
Having you is enough for me.

07:46.040 --> 07:46.640
Here, Yuanbao.

07:46.640 --> 07:48.100
Get up and have some water.

07:49.600 --> 07:51.530
Come on, get up and have some water.

07:53.640 --> 07:54.280
Here.

07:57.760 --> 07:59.080
You sprained your hand. Don't move.

07:59.080 --> 07:59.880
Let me do it.

07:59.880 --> 08:00.740
Here, Grandma.

08:10.400 --> 08:11.040
Well,

08:11.400 --> 08:13.600
I'll go help auntie cook. You guys talk.

08:24.720 --> 08:25.980
What's wrong with you?

08:26.400 --> 08:27.200
Nothing.

08:29.040 --> 08:30.760
Were you worried about me?

08:31.720 --> 08:33.200
Who's worried about you?

08:34.120 --> 08:35.520
Don't flatter yourself.

08:37.520 --> 08:38.720
Heartless.

08:45.800 --> 08:46.600
Blockhead.

08:48.480 --> 08:51.080
Well, I'll go help mom cook.

08:59.720 --> 09:00.720
Don't you know

09:01.760 --> 09:03.680
you almost lost your own life?

09:07.120 --> 09:08.080
I'm sorry.

09:19.520 --> 09:20.560
How is Qiao Yan?

09:21.840 --> 09:24.300
She just took her medicine and went to sleep.

09:25.280 --> 09:27.010
I don't mind you laughing at me,

09:27.760 --> 09:28.960
but it's all our fault

09:30.000 --> 09:31.320
that Xiaoyan

09:32.080 --> 09:33.480
ended up like this today.

09:33.520 --> 09:34.840
She is a good kid.

09:35.840 --> 09:38.560
Unfortunately, she didn't have good parents.

09:39.360 --> 09:40.420
Qiao Yan's father,

09:40.640 --> 09:42.100
have you ever hit Qiao Yan?

09:42.960 --> 09:44.200
It's all my fault.

09:45.240 --> 09:46.840
It's because of the alcohol.

09:47.560 --> 09:49.480
I swear I will never drink again.

09:49.560 --> 09:51.760
I won't touch a drop of alcohol for the rest of my life.

09:51.760 --> 09:53.680
I'm not human if I drink again.

09:59.080 --> 10:02.040
Your promises could fill a book.

10:02.800 --> 10:04.800
What's the point of saying all this?

10:04.960 --> 10:06.160
Let's get a divorce.

10:11.280 --> 10:12.880
What are you talking about?

10:13.600 --> 10:14.660
Qiao Yan's mother.

10:15.960 --> 10:17.280
I think

10:18.760 --> 10:21.320
you two should talk calmly.

10:21.880 --> 10:23.340
The top priority right now

10:23.480 --> 10:24.940
is to untie Qiao Yan's knot

10:25.320 --> 10:26.520
and cure her illness.

10:27.360 --> 10:28.840
I was too weak before,

10:30.080 --> 10:32.010
and failed to protect my daughter.

10:32.400 --> 10:34.520
I will only live for Xiaoyan from now on.

10:34.520 --> 10:36.520
As long as it's good for my daughter,

10:37.880 --> 10:39.440
I'd even give my life.

10:51.800 --> 10:52.860
Qiao Yan's father.

10:53.200 --> 10:54.240
A man

10:54.680 --> 10:57.000
who can bring himself to hurt his dearest wife and child

10:57.000 --> 10:58.130
is truly heartless.

10:59.320 --> 11:00.280
He doesn't even deserve to be called a man,

11:00.280 --> 11:01.720
let alone a human.

11:03.440 --> 11:04.770
That's all I have to say.

11:05.560 --> 11:06.820
You're on your own now.

11:29.080 --> 11:31.000
After modified electroconvulsive therapy,

11:31.000 --> 11:33.560
some temporary memory loss does indeed occur.

11:33.560 --> 11:35.120
But as time passes,

11:35.480 --> 11:37.640
those memories will slowly return.

11:37.760 --> 11:38.960
Don't worry too much.

11:44.320 --> 11:45.800
Besides the phone,

11:46.240 --> 11:48.520
I clearly wrote a few letters.

11:49.320 --> 11:50.200
But...

11:51.920 --> 11:54.040
What on earth did I write?

11:54.800 --> 11:56.860
Why don't I remember anything at all?

12:02.200 --> 12:04.060
Look outside the bedroom window!

12:13.560 --> 12:14.720
Qiao Yan.

12:14.960 --> 12:16.760
We love you.

12:16.960 --> 12:19.680
We're waiting for you to come back to us.

12:23.720 --> 12:25.600
Qiao Yan, we love you.

12:25.680 --> 12:28.040
You are not fighting alone.

12:28.880 --> 12:30.600
Qiao Yan, love you!

12:30.720 --> 12:32.650
We are waiting for you to come back.

12:32.840 --> 12:33.600
Qiao Yan.

12:33.920 --> 12:35.880
We will always be your best friends.

12:35.880 --> 12:38.040
Qiao Yan, we love you.

12:38.160 --> 12:40.690
We will always be your strongest supporters.

12:41.280 --> 12:43.760
Qiao Yan, remember the saying,

12:43.800 --> 12:45.000
it's no big deal.

12:46.480 --> 12:48.000
Stay strong, Qiao Yan!

12:48.880 --> 12:50.600
Come on, Qiao Yan!

12:50.680 --> 12:51.480
Qiao Yan,

12:51.600 --> 12:53.240
eat well, drink well,

12:53.520 --> 12:55.320
and don't let things bother you.

12:55.520 --> 12:56.960
Stay strong, Qiao Yan.

12:57.040 --> 12:58.280
You are the best.

13:54.560 --> 13:57.880
Qiao Yan, we love you.

13:57.960 --> 14:01.120
We will love you forever and ever.

14:47.400 --> 14:48.460
Hello, little one.

14:48.600 --> 14:49.800
Do you want a balloon?

14:51.400 --> 14:52.280
Is a pink one okay?

14:52.280 --> 14:52.680
Yes.

14:52.760 --> 14:53.760
Okay, here you go.

15:29.000 --> 15:31.680
God endowed humans with many abilities.

15:32.200 --> 15:34.720
The greatest one is love.

15:35.040 --> 15:38.160
It can melt glaciers and cross mountains and seas,

15:38.400 --> 15:41.160
nourish all things, and create miracles.

15:41.520 --> 15:43.760
Fortunately, we are still here.

15:44.400 --> 15:47.040
Fortunately, love is still here.

15:59.320 --> 16:00.640
I bought some fruits.

16:01.480 --> 16:04.920
There are kiwis and dragon fruit that Xiaoyan likes,

16:05.000 --> 16:05.840
and mangoes.

16:06.280 --> 16:08.320
Remember to eat them.

16:15.240 --> 16:15.880
By the way.

16:19.520 --> 16:23.160
Here are the bank cards and the rest of the cash.

16:23.720 --> 16:25.520
I'll leave them here for you two.

16:26.440 --> 16:27.240
If,

16:29.560 --> 16:30.680
after the New Year,

16:33.960 --> 16:36.320
you still want to get a divorce,

16:39.120 --> 16:39.920
I agree.

16:41.960 --> 16:42.920
The house

16:45.480 --> 16:46.480
and the money

16:47.160 --> 16:48.240
will be left to you.

16:50.480 --> 16:51.940
I will leave with nothing.

17:02.560 --> 17:03.290
I'm leaving.

17:26.680 --> 17:27.560
Did you call me?

17:36.640 --> 17:37.640
It's so cold.

17:38.120 --> 17:39.580
Where are you going alone?

17:40.920 --> 17:42.080
Stay.

17:43.440 --> 17:44.640
I'm sorry.

17:46.960 --> 17:48.160
I'm sorry.

17:50.920 --> 17:52.120
I'm sorry.

18:48.200 --> 18:49.160
My father

18:49.200 --> 18:51.440
is the best father in the world.

18:51.960 --> 18:54.090
He would take me to the amusement park,

18:54.200 --> 18:55.520
buy me cake,

18:56.160 --> 18:57.800
help me with my homework,

18:58.000 --> 19:00.360
and act like a clown to make me happy.

19:03.240 --> 19:04.720
Every time I got sick,

19:04.800 --> 19:06.920
Dad would stay by my side,

19:07.040 --> 19:09.720
give me water and medicine,

19:10.160 --> 19:13.040
and tell me a lot of jokes.

19:13.920 --> 19:16.360
He was like an encyclopedia,

19:16.480 --> 19:17.840
knowing everything.

19:22.360 --> 19:25.320
But I don't know when it started,

19:25.760 --> 19:28.020
Dad stopped smiling as much as he used to.

19:28.160 --> 19:29.800
He no longer told me stories

19:30.200 --> 19:32.080
or helped me with my homework.

19:32.400 --> 19:34.120
He started drinking a lot

19:34.280 --> 19:35.560
and losing his temper.

19:36.200 --> 19:38.400
He didn't seem like my dad anymore.

19:39.520 --> 19:41.320
My dad is gone.

19:43.200 --> 19:44.640
I miss him so much.

19:47.480 --> 19:49.200
I really want to find him.

20:15.320 --> 20:16.050
Sweetheart.

20:17.960 --> 20:19.280
Daddy's home.

20:19.840 --> 20:22.640
I'm sorry. I'm late.

20:23.840 --> 20:24.760
Don't worry.

20:25.440 --> 20:27.160
I've pulled myself together.

20:28.160 --> 20:29.360
I promise you,

20:30.240 --> 20:31.760
I will never drink again.

20:34.600 --> 20:37.680
I will love you with all my heart,

20:38.080 --> 20:39.000
and your mom.

21:24.360 --> 21:26.360
Forgive me, okay?

21:52.560 --> 21:54.420
The first semester of junior year

21:54.560 --> 21:56.560
ended with a bang just like that.

21:59.560 --> 22:01.090
Some people have been here.

22:06.240 --> 22:09.080
Some people have left.

22:22.280 --> 22:23.200
Let's go, bro.

22:47.720 --> 22:49.800
Some people remain the same.

22:50.520 --> 22:53.440
But some people have changed.

23:07.400 --> 23:08.840
Tomorrow is New Year's Eve.

23:08.840 --> 23:10.160
Why are you still taking extra classes?

23:10.160 --> 23:12.420
Doesn't your cram school have a holiday?

23:13.240 --> 23:14.240
Don't mention it.

23:14.840 --> 23:16.320
The cram school is on holiday.

23:16.320 --> 23:17.580
My mom found me a tutor.

23:17.680 --> 23:19.540
One-on-one, tutoring me at home.

23:19.880 --> 23:22.080
If the teacher didn't have to celebrate the New Year,

23:22.080 --> 23:23.160
I guess my mom would wish

23:23.160 --> 23:25.560
I could have classes even on New Year's Eve.

23:26.120 --> 23:28.120
Your mom is torturing you like this?

23:28.320 --> 23:30.120
You know my parents.

23:30.600 --> 23:32.880
They firmly believe that God rewards the diligent,

23:32.880 --> 23:35.240
and no pain, no gain.

23:35.960 --> 23:38.040
Didn't I drop three places in the exam this time?

23:38.040 --> 23:39.300
Guess what my mom said.

23:39.800 --> 23:41.720
My mom said if I don't make progress

23:41.720 --> 23:42.840
in the next exam,

23:43.040 --> 23:46.200
so she can just let me stay at the cram school and not go home.

23:46.200 --> 23:47.280
Compared to that,

23:47.400 --> 23:49.330
my grandmother is way more gentle.

23:50.000 --> 23:51.640
That's why I envy you.

23:55.400 --> 23:56.530
You two princesses,

23:56.640 --> 23:58.300
the food is ready. Time to eat.

24:08.080 --> 24:10.520
Wait for me downstairs after you finish eating.

24:10.520 --> 24:12.120
I have something to tell you.

24:12.480 --> 24:14.720
What a coincidence. I also have something to tell you.

24:14.720 --> 24:15.440
Really?

24:16.560 --> 24:17.720
See you later then.

24:31.240 --> 24:31.960
Blockhead.

24:33.280 --> 24:34.280
Ruirui went back.

24:35.240 --> 24:37.170
Let's go. I'll take you somewhere.

24:37.360 --> 24:38.880
Didn't you have something to say to me?

24:38.880 --> 24:39.880
Where are we going all of a sudden?

24:39.880 --> 24:40.880
Just come with me.

24:53.520 --> 24:54.760
So late at night,

24:55.120 --> 24:56.520
why did you bring me here?

24:56.840 --> 24:57.900
Diamond Princess,

24:58.160 --> 25:00.760
do you still remember the promise we made at 18?

25:01.600 --> 25:03.200
Diamond Princess.

25:11.600 --> 25:13.360
Yuanbao, Yuanbao, don't cry.

25:13.400 --> 25:14.480
Where are you hurt?

25:14.520 --> 25:15.360
What's wrong?

25:16.440 --> 25:17.400
Yuanbao, look.

25:17.440 --> 25:18.920
Is that a diamond?

25:20.400 --> 25:21.440
Where?

25:26.680 --> 25:29.120
I've heard the story of the Diamond Princess.

25:29.120 --> 25:30.250
Have you heard of it?

25:30.480 --> 25:31.680
Diamond Princess?

25:32.080 --> 25:32.520
Yes.

25:32.600 --> 25:34.640
A long time ago, there was a little girl.

25:34.640 --> 25:37.480
Her tears could turn into shining diamonds.

25:37.640 --> 25:39.880
So people called her the Diamond Princess.

25:39.880 --> 25:42.480
One day, an old man with a white beard found her

25:42.720 --> 25:45.160
and told her that when she turned 18,

25:45.320 --> 25:47.120
if she brought her diamond tears

25:47.200 --> 25:49.360
to the same place on the same day,

25:49.560 --> 25:52.220
she would receive a mysterious gift from an elf.

25:52.520 --> 25:53.800
What mysterious gift?

25:54.040 --> 25:55.120
I don't know.

25:55.160 --> 25:56.480
But look at your tears.

25:56.520 --> 25:58.720
They've turned into shining diamonds.

25:58.840 --> 26:01.280
That means you are also a Diamond Princess.

26:01.320 --> 26:03.640
You have to keep this diamond safe.

26:03.680 --> 26:05.320
When you turn 18,

26:05.640 --> 26:06.840
we'll come back here.

26:06.840 --> 26:07.680
Then we'll know

26:07.680 --> 26:09.400
what gift the elf gives you.

26:10.880 --> 26:12.920
You must come too.

26:13.040 --> 26:13.800
Definitely.

26:14.680 --> 26:15.940
Don't even mention it.

26:16.000 --> 26:19.000
I treasured that piece of broken glass for a long time.

26:19.240 --> 26:21.880
I even really thought it was a diamond at one point.

26:21.880 --> 26:23.520
To get more diamonds,

26:23.640 --> 26:26.160
I secretly cried countless times.

26:26.480 --> 26:28.800
My eyes got swollen from crying so many times,

26:28.800 --> 26:30.360
but I never succeeded once.

26:34.720 --> 26:35.720
Actually,

26:36.480 --> 26:37.400
this story

26:38.080 --> 26:39.480
isn't completely fake.

26:40.000 --> 26:40.680
What?

26:41.280 --> 26:42.640
Are there really elves

26:42.640 --> 26:44.370
delivering mysterious gifts?

26:44.440 --> 26:46.480
Come on, try closing your eyes.

26:47.080 --> 26:47.840
What for?

26:48.640 --> 26:50.500
Just close them when I tell you to.

26:50.960 --> 26:52.880
So mysterious.

27:08.600 --> 27:09.680
The elf says

27:09.840 --> 27:11.480
you can open your eyes now.

27:29.440 --> 27:30.320
Studying?

27:30.640 --> 27:31.320
Auntie.

27:32.760 --> 27:35.200
Dad, Mom, what's wrong?

27:36.360 --> 27:37.640
There's something.

27:37.840 --> 27:39.240
Grandma, Dad, and I

27:39.280 --> 27:41.340
have been discussing for a long time.

27:41.760 --> 27:44.220
We want to hear your and Yuanbao's opinions.

27:48.560 --> 27:49.520
What is it?

27:51.360 --> 27:52.080
Honey,

27:52.480 --> 27:53.740
let's sit down to talk.

27:54.000 --> 27:55.200
Okay, let's sit down.

28:01.040 --> 28:01.960
It's like this.

28:02.400 --> 28:03.400
As you know,

28:03.560 --> 28:06.520
your dad's previous job in the UK was pretty good,

28:06.840 --> 28:08.640
and the salary was substantial.

28:09.440 --> 28:11.100
But after returning to China,

28:11.200 --> 28:12.280
up to now,

28:12.360 --> 28:14.160
he hasn't found a suitable job.

28:14.920 --> 28:17.760
You know our family's financial situation.

28:19.920 --> 28:22.880
Seeing as you two are about to go to college,

28:23.360 --> 28:25.800
the expenses will be huge.

28:26.320 --> 28:27.640
So we discussed it

28:28.120 --> 28:31.800
and decided to have your dad go back to the UK to work after the New Year.

28:31.800 --> 28:32.600
This way,

28:32.600 --> 28:35.400
our family's financial burden will be lightened.

28:35.840 --> 28:36.520
Son.

28:37.560 --> 28:38.320
I know.

28:38.760 --> 28:41.200
I've been working out of town these years,

28:41.640 --> 28:43.560
and I'm rarely home to accompany you.

28:43.560 --> 28:45.320
Even when the accident happened last time,

28:45.320 --> 28:46.760
I rushed back late.

28:48.360 --> 28:50.560
Actually, I'm really conflicted.

28:50.920 --> 28:52.180
Leaving you all at home

28:53.240 --> 28:55.960
makes me feel really guilty.

28:56.400 --> 28:58.680
Dad, just focus on your work.

28:59.120 --> 28:59.960
I support you.

29:00.080 --> 29:02.000
Yes, Uncle. I support you too.

29:03.880 --> 29:06.440
Didn't you complain about your dad to me before,

29:06.440 --> 29:08.560
saying he's always busy with work

29:08.640 --> 29:09.920
and doesn't care about you?

29:09.920 --> 29:10.600
This time,

29:10.640 --> 29:12.480
why did you agree so readily?

29:15.160 --> 29:16.360
I've grown up.

29:16.680 --> 29:18.610
I'm definitely more sensible now.

29:18.840 --> 29:21.520
Dad works outside for our family,

29:21.720 --> 29:22.480
for Grandma,

29:22.600 --> 29:23.530
and for Yuanbao.

29:24.240 --> 29:25.160
I understand.

29:26.800 --> 29:28.160
See? What did I tell you?

29:28.320 --> 29:30.080
I said our son would understand,

29:30.080 --> 29:32.610
but you've been agonizing over this for days.

29:33.320 --> 29:35.800
Yes, our Qingyun has grown up

29:35.960 --> 29:37.090
and is sensible now.

29:38.240 --> 29:39.280
Then,

29:39.320 --> 29:40.520
I'll book the flight.

29:41.680 --> 29:43.000
Leaving so soon?

29:43.600 --> 29:44.280
Yes.

29:44.880 --> 29:46.080
I have to go early,

29:46.440 --> 29:48.840
otherwise someone else might take the job.

29:49.160 --> 29:49.760
By the way,

29:50.160 --> 29:51.090
you and Yuanbao,

29:51.200 --> 29:53.660
you must go to school and come back together,

29:53.760 --> 29:55.440
so you can look out for each other.

29:55.440 --> 29:57.960
And you two need to do your best

29:58.040 --> 29:58.900
and study hard.

29:59.960 --> 30:00.960
Don't worry, Dad.

30:01.440 --> 30:02.570
Don't worry, Uncle.

30:02.640 --> 30:04.440
I'll keep an eye on Mutou for you.

30:06.840 --> 30:07.880
So,

30:08.000 --> 30:10.200
it's passed unanimously by our family.

30:11.360 --> 30:11.840
Come on,

30:11.880 --> 30:13.560
I'll go pack your dad's luggage.

30:13.560 --> 30:14.620
You two study hard.

30:14.640 --> 30:15.800
Study hard.

30:17.280 --> 30:18.280
Study hard.

30:32.200 --> 30:34.360
Mutou, Zhicheng's top brother

30:34.880 --> 30:37.280
usually acts like he's afraid of nothing.

30:37.760 --> 30:39.760
But knowing his dad is going far away

30:40.280 --> 30:41.800
and facing separation,

30:42.040 --> 30:43.880
he still acts like a child,

30:43.960 --> 30:45.760
feeling wronged and sad.

30:46.800 --> 30:49.600
Is it true that no matter how old someone gets,

30:50.000 --> 30:51.680
when facing their parents,

30:52.080 --> 30:54.120
they instantly become a child?

30:55.440 --> 30:56.880
What does that feel like?

30:57.760 --> 30:59.440
I really want to experience it.
